
* offtovma - converts file offset to vma mappings

* SYNOPSIS - 
			offtovma [-h | --help ]
			         [-c | --core ]
							 [-v | --version ]
							 [-o | --offset ]

* DESCRIPTION -
	offtovma displays various load segments/vmas available in the core file.

* OPTIONS

	-h
	--help - Prints the help string

	-v
	--version - Prints the verstion string

	-c
	--core - The core file name

	-o
	--offset - The offset within the file that needs vma mappings

  -d
  --dump - Emulate octal dump but print VMA instead of file offsets.

